00:15:48.504 --> 00:15:55.604
- Well I had to make it clear to the
board what we're trying to do, and

00:15:56.624 --> 00:15:59.404
the management team knew our gross
margins were gonna get crushed.

00:16:00.684 --> 00:16:04.604
So you could imagine a world
where GeForce would carry

00:16:04.644 --> 00:16:07.784
the burden of CUDA and
none of the gamers would

00:16:08.144 --> 00:16:12.044
appreciate it and none of the gamers
would pay for it. You know, they only pay

00:16:12.144 --> 00:16:15.904
certain price and it doesn't matter what
your cost is. And so the... You know,

00:16:16.004 --> 00:16:19.784
we, we increased our cost
by 50% and that con-

00:16:20.144 --> 00:16:24.104
consumed... And we were a 35%
