00:16:37.864 --> 00:16:41.583
so you could, you could reason your
way into being able to afford this,

00:16:42.284 --> 00:16:44.744
But it still took... It took a decade.

00:16:45.064 --> 00:16:48.544
- But that, but that's more of, like, conversation
with the board convincing them, but you

00:16:48.564 --> 00:16:54.694
psychologically- ... as NVIDIA's
continued to make bold bets

00:16:56.444 --> 00:17:00.944
that predict the future, and in part,
especially now, define the future.

00:17:01.744 --> 00:17:05.144
So I'm almost looking for wisdom about

00:17:05.744 --> 00:17:09.664
how you're able to make those decisions,
to make leaps- ... like that as a company.

00:17:14.864 --> 00:17:20.794
- Well, first of all I'm informed
by a lot of curiosity.

00:17:21.584 --> 00:17:25.754
At some point, there's a
reasoning system that,

00:17:26.694 --> 00:17:33.624
that convinces me, so clearly this outcome
