system is completely

00:31:53.664 --> 00:31:57.444
different than the previous
one, and it's got all these new

00:31:57.484 --> 00:32:01.324
components in it. And the reason for that
is because the last one was designed to run

00:32:02.084 --> 00:32:08.364
MoE large language models, inference.
