00:34:21.444 --> 00:34:24.653
microwave, reads it,
instantly becomes an expert.

00:34:24.724 --> 00:34:28.214
And so it uses it. And
so I think the... I just

00:34:28.244 --> 00:34:34.424
described, in fact, almost all
of the properties of OpenClaw.

00:34:35.084 --> 00:34:38.864
You know, that it's gonna use tools, that it's
gonna access files, it's gonna be able to do

00:34:38.904 --> 00:34:42.774
research. It has I/O subsystem.
And when you're done

00:34:42.804 --> 00:34:45.873
reasoning through it, reasoning
about it in that way,

00:34:46.744 --> 00:34:53.084
Then you say, "Oh, my gosh, the impact
